Episode notes

In the first podcast of 2021, we kickstart the Economy & Finance Network’s pamphlet campaign on the Economic lens to reclaiming the Heartlands: 100 years since Labour's first government.

Sign up to our new newsletter! http://eepurl.com/heI28X

Speakers:

Alex Mitchell – Vice-Chair of the Yorkshire and the Humberside Network https://twitter.com/AlMitchell89

Grahame Anderson – Chair of the North East Network https://twitter.com/GrahameAnders

Marie Hill – Secretary of the North West Network https://twitter.com/Marie__hill

Matthew Suddart – Chair of the North West Network https://twitter.com/Matt_Suddart

Producer:

Louie Marlow https://twitter.com/louiemarlow

This event was recorded on Wednesday 6th January.

To all our listeners: we want you in our podcast, so if you’re passionate about a topic just get in touch with us at [email protected]

If you want to contribute to this pamphlet do not hesitate to contact the Economy & Finance Network at [email protected]
